<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Google Account Authentication Successful</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .details {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }
      .details p {
        margin: 4px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .google-logo {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(66,133,244,0.15);
      }
      .note {
        background: #fffbe6;
        border-left: 5px solid #fbbc05;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin: 18px 0;
        color: #b08500;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Hello, <%= name %>!</h2>
      <p>
        You have successfully <strong>authenticate</strong> using your Google account. We’re excited to have you join the Rental House Management System community!
      </p>

      <div class="details">
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #2c3e50;"><strong>Account Details</strong></p>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date || 'N/A' %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="note">
        <strong>Note:</strong> For the best experience, please update your profile details (such as <b>role</b> and <b>phone number</b>) after authentication. We use default values for these fields when you authenticate with Google.
      </div>

      <p>
        Thank you for choosing Rental House Management System! If you have any questions or need help, our support team is here for you.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for joining us!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The Rental House Management Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Rental House Management System
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>